reviewText: So one of the things my mom gave me for Christmas was a $100.00 gift card to Walmart. I've been wanting to get movies, I seen this upon the new releases and I seen that Paris Hilton voiced one of the characters and I bought it. I adore Paris very much. For $10.00 this movie was great!  I recommend this to any animal lovers. Definitely worth the money!

reviewText: Another charming entry in the Dog Who Saved Christmas collection comes from Anchor Bay.  This time, the Bannister family is spending their vacation at a Rocky Mountain resort and familiar thieves led by Dean Cain make a return visit.  This time, Uncle Randy (Casper Van Diem) is part of the mix and mayhem.This film is cute and is suitable for young viewers from ages 5 to 12.  Older movie viewers will enjoy it for its' lightness and good casting.Bravo Anchor Bay Entertainment.Tim Lasiuta
